Interface FieldValidator<D>

  • Type Parameters:
    D - Type of input data
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AuthorizedKeyValidator, BadKeyFactory, EmailListInput.EmailListValidator, IntegerSetInput.IntegerSetValidator, NewFieldInput.NewFieldValidator, NewTableInput.NewTableNameValidator, NoHtmlValidator, NoSpaceFieldValidator, ObjectListInput.ObjectListValidator, ParseFactoryValidator, PatternTextInput.PatternFieldValidator, RestrictedEmailFieldValidator, RsaKeyValidator, ServiceAllowedEmailFieldValidator, TokenFieldValidator, TotpCodeAuthComposite.CodeValidator, URLInput.URLValidator

    public interface FieldValidator<D>
    Interface for an additional external validator that can be added to a Field. As FieldValidators are stored in Sets it is good practice to implement #hashCode() and #equals(Object). Note that a FieldValidator could throw a MissingFieldException
